Student portal.

Generallay every student and teachers  have  a student login portal.

Student

Every student have to register to the student portal.After Registraion they  will get one email in the mail user id will be there for their login.

 
	In student portal student can login by using  student id and password 
	student can see all exam marks.
	They can submit their project files to respective staff.

Notifications
	After teacher added marks or appr/rej projects student will get notification by email

Teacher 

student portal for respective teacher also.
 The teacher have to register in student portal with teacher_id and email id.Teacher will get login id by email as like a student.

	The teacher can add mark for respective class students.
	Teacher can reject or approve their projects with remarks

Notification
	Teacher will get notification by email after the student submitted the projects
